This is the root for 2.x development.  It currently contains the following
directories:

util - all utility projects:
* animation
* connection
* dom
* dragdrop
* event

widget - all widget projects:
* autocomplete
* calendar
* menu
* overlay
* slider
* treeview

css - all CSS-specific projects
* font
* grid
* reset

build - raw versions of build files for all components
* animation
* autocomplete
* calendar
* connection
* dom
* dragdrop
* event
* menu
* overlay
* slider
* treeview

example of a component subdirectory:
-- widget
| |
| -- calendar
| | |
    -- build
| | | |
      -- calendar.js (raw, commented source)
| | | |
| | | -- calendar-min.js (minified source)
| | |
| | -- src
| | | |
      -- css
| | | | |
        -- calendar.css
| | | |
      -img
| | | | |
        -- callt.gif
| | | |
      -- js
| | | | |
| | | | -- Calendar.js

example of a build subdirectory:
-- build
| |
| -- calendar
| | |
    -- calendar.js (raw, commented source)
| | | |
| | -- assets (local copies of akamaized css and img assets)
| | | |
| | | -- callt.gif     
| | | |
      -- calendar.css
